<view class="page">
  <view class="research-hero">
    <text class="eyebrow">RESEARCH CENTER</text>
    <text class="h1">GeoGi 研究中心</text>
    <text class="lead">围绕 GEO、AI 可见度、品牌实体和信源结构，沉淀可被企业团队直接使用的方法论。</text>
  </view>

  <view class="category-row">
    <button
      wx:for="{{categories}}"
      wx:key="*this"
      data-category="{{item}}"
      bindtap="changeCategory"
      class="category-pill {{activeCategory == item ? 'active' : ''}}"
    >
      {{item}}
    </button>
  </view>

  <view wx:if="{{usingFallback}}" class="fallback-note">
    <text>当前展示内置示例内容；正式上线后将从飞书内容表同步。</text>
  </view>

  <view class="section list">
    <view class="article-card card" wx:for="{{filteredArticles}}" wx:key="id" data-id="{{item.id}}" bindtap="openArticle">
      <view class="article-cover">
        <text>{{item.category}}</text>
      </view>
      <text class="article-date">{{item.date}}</text>
      <text class="article-title">{{item.title}}</text>
      <text class="body">{{item.desc}}</text>
      <text class="article-link">阅读全文</text>
    </view>
  </view>

  <view class="section path-card card">
    <text class="path-title">建议阅读路径</text>
    <view class="path-row">
      <text class="path-num">01</text>
      <text class="path-copy">先理解 GEO 与传统 SEO 的差异</text>
    </view>
    <view class="path-row">
      <text class="path-num">02</text>
      <text class="path-copy">再梳理品牌实体和内容证据</text>
    </view>
    <view class="path-row">
      <text class="path-num">03</text>
      <text class="path-copy">最后建设能被引用的权威信源</text>
    </view>
  </view>
</view>
